{"metadata":{"images":[{"identifier":"ic_design_token_figma_component.png","type":"icon"}],"externalID":"OUDSTokensComponent","roleHeading":"Library","modules":[{"name":"Tokens for components"}],"title":"Tokens for components","symbolKind":"module","role":"collection"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"These ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" are defined for components and refer to semantic tokens or raw tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"They can be seen as a kind of bridge between components and in the end primitive values of the design kit.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["🧬 Core version: 1.9.0"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Thus if a component need to change for example its ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"background color","type":"text"}]},{"text":", and if a ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component token"}]},{"text":" is used for it, then only the value of this ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"token","type":"text"}]},{"text":" should be changed without any modification on the ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"component","type":"text"}]},{"text":" definition.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Components","type":"text"}]},{"text":" use ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}]},{"text":" exposed through the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" thanks to token providers to get their style values.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components tokens are defined and gathered inside "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift protocol"}]},{"type":"text","text":" so as to be exposed then through implementation of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" thanks to dedicated tokens providers."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because we choose to split responsabilities and objects into their own modules, we faced troubles to make possible for children themes or providers to override properties declared in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"protocols","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and defined in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"extensions","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"That is the reason why tokens are exposed as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@objc open"},{"type":"text","text":" to be available and overridable anywhere."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Example with ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Declare some component tokens for buttons with properties they must apply","public protocol ButtonComponentTokens {","    var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { get }","    var borderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { get }","    var borderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { get }","    var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticToken { get }","    var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { get }","}","","\/\/ There is an existing provider for such tokens","open class OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider { }","","\/\/ Define the components tokens exposed through the theme thanks to provider","extension OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider: ButtonComponentTokens {","","    \/\/ Raw tokens can be used","","    @objc open var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._600 }","    ","    \/\/ And also semantic tokens","","    @objc open var borderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthThicker }","    @objc open var borderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.radiusMedium }","    @objc open var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","    @objc open var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSpacious }","}","","\/\/ This provider is then exposed through OUDSTheme as an AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"text":"How to use component tokens","anchor":"How-to-use-component-tokens","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In fact, the component tokens are declared and gathered in ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift protocol","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to force any theme to implement them, and also to allow any theme to expose such properties whathever the implementation of the theme is, across providers."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" have for values ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"raw tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"semantic tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", and in the end for values primitive types, and all these tokens are declared with ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"type aliases","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" refering all together, you can handle a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component token","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" directly in your view because the final value will be used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Thus, get the theme and call the needed property with some helpers.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct SomeView: View {","","    @Environment(\\.theme) private var theme \/\/ Supposed you used in your root view the `OUDSThemeableView` to register the theme","    @Environment(\\.colorScheme) private var colorScheme","","    var body: some View {","        Button {","            \/\/ Some action","        } label: {","            Text(\"Some label\")","                .cornerRadius(theme.button.borderRadius)","        }","        .padding(.leading, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronStart)","        .padding(.trailing, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd)","        .background(theme.button.colorBgStrongEnabledMono)","        .overlay(","            RoundedRectangle(cornerRadius: theme.button.borderRadius)","                .stroke(Color.blue, lineWidth: theme.button.borderWidthDefault)","        )","    }","\/*","    - The theme provides border semantic tokens \"borderRadius\" and \"borderWidthDefault\"","    - The theme provides a color semantic token \"colorBgStrongEnabledMono\"","    - The theme provides spaces semantic token \"spacePaddingInlineChevronStart\" and \"spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd\"","*\/","}","","\/\/ Do not forget in your app to use the `OUDSThemeableView` for your theme, e.g. `OrangeTheme`","@main","struct DesignToolbox: App {","","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","                ...","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The components tokens are wrapped in tokens provider acessible through the themes:"}]},{"type":"table","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components tokens provider"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Target component"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"bar","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For bars components like bottom and navigation bars"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For badges like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBadge"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For buttons like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bulletList"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For list of elements with bullets","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"checkbox"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For checkboxes like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckbox"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"text":" and their indeterminate variants","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"chip","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For chips like "},{"code":"OUDSSuggestionChip","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"OUDSFilterChip","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"controlItem"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Shared and used for switch, checkbox and radio items layouts"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"divider"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For dividers like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSHorizontalDivider"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSVerticalDivider"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"icon","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For components containing icons like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTag"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"link","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For links like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"pinCodeInput","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"quantityInput","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"radioButton"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For radio components like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadio"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioItem"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selectInput"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"skeleton"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"switch","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For switch components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"tag","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For tag components like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTag","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inputTag"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For input tag components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSInputTag"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"textArea"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For text area components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTextArea"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"textInput"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineCont